headline: ONEOK Q4 Earnings Top Estimates, Revenues Rise Year Over Year
summary: OKE Q4 EPS beat estimates as revenues jump 29% YoY, but margins dip and the 2026 outlook guides steady earnings and a $3B capex plan.
